      <title>南非的领导者看到了增值税替代方案的昏暗前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/south-africa-s-leader-sees-dim-prospect-for-vat-hike-alternative</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨（Cyril Ramaphosa）表示，国家财政部正在寻找各种选择，以避免不得不提高增值税，但逃脱这种增长的前景是昏暗的。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/south-africa-s-leader-sees-dim-prospect-for-vat-hike-alternative</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 16:05:07 GMT</pubDate>
