      <title>Evercore ISI是华尔街最新的公司，可削减S＆amp; P 500目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/evercore-isi-is-latest-firm-on-wall-street-to-cut-s-p-500-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在S＆amp; P 500指数在短短两天内就消除了5.4万亿美元的贸易战争恐惧后，Evercore ISI加入了其他华尔街公司，表示在2025年的目标和Mdash中过于乐观。但是仍然看到股票按年底划分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-06/evercore-isi-is-latest-firm-on-wall-street-to-cut-s-p-500-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Apr 2025 15:34:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
